Training Competitions: How-To

 Coach Bres July 20, 2017 Athletics,  Coaching,  Football Leave a Comment

So you want to run a training competition? Great! Coaches across the country utilize competitions every summer to incentivize athletes, increase participation, and build team culture. But how do you put it together? While a really great tool in theory, a training competition can be extremely difficult endeavor to actually administer on your own. The key is to keep it … 
