Article reposted with permission from Robert Williams of the Detroit Lakes Tribune. View the Original Here. Detroit Lakes middle school and high school athletes are putting aside what could be a leisurely summer to become more explosive athletically as part of the Laker Speed and Strength program sponsored by the Laker Sports Boosters. While kids could be out on the pontoon and … 
